  m_text: "Detective Schmit Sanders spent years chasing rumours from forgotten towns
    on the edge of nowhere. When reports surfaced about travelers vanishing near
    an abandoned roadside hotel, he followed the trail without hesitation. The building
    wasn\u2019t on any official map, yet its lamps burned every night. He checked
    in to investigate. The doors locked behind him. The staff vanished. The rooms
    shifted. Now Schmit had a clear understanding, this hotel wasn\u2019t found.\n"
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 9262c88b875c24d41bdba58fed431648, type: 2}
  m_sharedMaterial: {fileID: 7078714273678001544, guid: 9262c88b875c24d41bdba58fed431648, type: 2}
